2026-05-13T23:21:25.2648906Z 217        <!--
2026-05-13T23:21:25.2649537Z 218            Override Google Play Billing's ProxyBillingActivity so the system
2026-05-13T23:21:25.2650481Z 219            cannot restore it from Recents or after process death with a
2026-05-13T23:21:25.2651374Z 220            stale Intent. The library's onCreate reads the PendingIntent
2026-05-13T23:21:25.2652269Z 221            extra without null-checking; if Android recreates the activity
2026-05-13T23:21:25.2653042Z 222            and the extra is missing, it NPEs on
2026-05-13T23:21:25.2653852Z 223            PendingIntent.getIntentSender(). noHistory + excludeFromRecents
2026-05-13T23:21:25.2654772Z 224            ensures the activity is finished as soon as it leaves the
2026-05-13T23:21:25.2655883Z 225            foreground and is never re-entered with a missing extra. See
