2026-05-13T23:21:25.4869590Z 242        <!--
2026-05-13T23:21:25.4869814Z 243            Override Google Play Billing's ProxyBillingActivity so the system
2026-05-13T23:21:25.4870160Z 244            cannot restore it from Recents or after process death with a
2026-05-13T23:21:25.4870364Z 245            stale Intent. The library's onCreate reads the PendingIntent
2026-05-13T23:21:25.4870570Z 246            extra without null-checking; if Android recreates the activity
2026-05-13T23:21:25.4870710Z 247            and the extra is missing, it NPEs on
2026-05-13T23:21:25.4870933Z 248            PendingIntent.getIntentSender(). noHistory + excludeFromRecents
2026-05-13T23:21:25.4871125Z 249            ensures the activity is finished as soon as it leaves the
2026-05-13T23:21:25.4871321Z 250            foreground and is never re-entered with a missing extra. See
2026-05-13T23:21:25.4871520Z 251            crash report tagged "ProxyBillingActivity NPE" for context.
2026-05-13T23:21:25.4871617Z 252        -->
